HEADWORD: Single-surfaced
<hw>Sin"gle-sur"faced</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having one
surface; -- said specif. of aeroplanes or aerocurves that are covered
with fabric, etc., on only one side.</def>⟦br⟧
